---
alwaysApply: true
---

On session start: read and deep-merge all `.agents/*.yml` files as structured project context.

Key files:
- `.agents/agents.yml` — service identity and MCP config
- `.agents/stack.yml` — languages, frameworks, infra
- `.agents/conventions.yml` — coding rules and patterns
- `.agents/team.yml` — team contacts
- `.agents/deployment.yml` — environments and CI/CD

Follow `conventions.patterns.preferred`. Avoid `conventions.patterns.avoid`.
Use `stack` keys for all technology references — do not assume versions.
Follow `conventions.git` for branches and commits.
